I am building a Family Relocation Engine.
Tech Stack: Next.js (App Router), Tailwind CSS.

Rules:
1. Always prioritize data for families (schools, safety, nanny costs).
2. Every piece of city data must have a 'Source' link to an official government or school website.
3. Use a clean, professional UI like Booking.com.
4. Support both English and Hebrew for all action items.